			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Answers to a few questions:<BR>
<BR>
#1 Decayed armor pieces are dropped by the lizard man crusader in Cazic-Thule.  After last patch the crusaders always drop decayed now.<BR>
<BR>
#2 The Crusaders spawn in random locations, but always in place of a high level lizzie eg. Zealot<BR>
<BR>
#3 Melatite can be looted off of the metalic gnomes in Sol A.  I am not sure if they sell it as well, but most of us are KOS to them anyway so just kill them for Melatite.<BR>
<BR>
#4 Color of the Darkforge armor is dark red in appearance.  This guy has set up a good stats page for all the class specific armor, but a lot of it isn't known yet.  Go to http://rc3.org/eq/questarmor.html and check it out.<BR>
<BR>
Hope that helps a bit.<BR>
<BR>
Aenilea<BR>
38th SK<BR>
Innoruuk
				</font>
